headline: United Rentals Stock Earns Relative Strength Rating Upgrade
summary: The Relative Strength (RS) Rating for United Rentals stock entered a new percentile Friday, with a rise from 74 to 82.  Is United Rentals Stock A Buy?  United Rentals stock has risen more than 5% past an 826.46 entry in a first-stage cup with handle, meaning it's extended and now out of a proper buy range.
